{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1687-11_103","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Le Papillion et l’Abeille. Fable","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", novembre 1687 [tome 16], p. 103-110","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},{"#":[{"#":{"value":"Le Pere Comire Jesuite, qui s’est acquis tant de reputation par la beauté de ses Vers Latins, a fait une Fable sur le Papillon, &amp; sur l’Abeille. Elle est extremement estimée, &amp; il ne faut pas s’en étonner, puis que tout ce que nous avons vû de luy, a ce tour aisé &amp; naturel que tout le monde recherche, &amp; qu’il est si difficile d’attraper. M","id":"/div/p[1]/#[0]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p[1]/#[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" Petit de Roüen à fait la traduction de cette Fable avec beaucoup de fidelité, &amp; je croy que vous n’aurez pas moins de plaisir à la lire, que vous en avez receu des ","id":"/div/p[1]/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dialogues Satyriques &amp; Moraux","id":"/div/p[1]/#[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":", dont il est l’Autheur, &amp; qui ont esté si approuvez du Public. Son jugement en cela se trouve tous les jours conforme à ce qui en fut dit d’avantageux il y a quelque temps dans la Republique des Lettres.","id":"/div/p[1]/#[4]/#"}}]}],"quote":{"label":{"#":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"LE PAPILLON","id":"/div/quote/label/#[0]/hi/#"}}},{"lb":{}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"ET L’ABEILLE","id":"/div/quote/label/#[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":".","id":"/div/quote/label/#[3]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"FABLE.","id":"/div/quote/label/#[5]/#"}}]},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un Jardin delicieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un Papillon tout glorieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De se voir les aisles dorées,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et superbement empourprées,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Admiroit la beauté des fleurs","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De mille sortes de couleurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À qui l’Aurore avec ses larmes","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit donné de nouveaux charmes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qu’elle répandoit exprés","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour leur rendre le teint plus frais.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" À l’heure que Phébus s’éveille","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Prés de luy se trouve une Abeille","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À laquelle il dit. Chere Sœur,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Goûtons, goûtons la douce odeur ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ces fleurs dont en abondance","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Flore icy s’est mise en dépense ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une si rare volupté","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rendons nostre cœur enchanté.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Aussi-tost s’élevant de terre","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il voltige sur le Parterre.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On eust dit, le voyant en l’air,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une fleur qui sçavoit voler,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tant ses couleurs d’or &amp; vermeilles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À celles des fleurs sont pareilles.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il les éfleuroit seulement,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans dessein, sans discernement.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelquefois sur la Violette,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Charmé de l’odeur, il se jette ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelquefois il baise en passant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un bouton de Rose naissant ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et le mouvement de ses aisles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Excite un vent aussi doux qu’elles.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur chaque fleur de ce Jardin","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il vole comme un vray Badin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les foulant toutes sans malice.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’Oeillet il court au Narcisse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis poussé d’un nouveau desir","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur l’Anemone il va dormir.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais son sommeil ne dure guere ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et d’une inquiete maniere,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Opiniâtre, sans repos,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De fleurs il change à tous propos.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De les caresser il s’empresse ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais incontinent il les laisse.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour toutes ainsi tour à tour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Son dégoust succede à l’Amour.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Tandis que ce fou se tourmente","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Abeille beaucoup plus prudente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sçachant mieux ce qu’elle fait,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des fleurs ne fait pas un joüet,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de leurs odeurs les plus fines","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne réjoüit pas ses narines,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ny ne vole pas à l’entour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vainement tout le long du jour ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais comme un Ouvrier habile,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Meslant l’agreable à l’utile,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle prend la Cire &amp; le Miel","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que sur leur teint répand le Ciel,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont l’influence les arrose,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pille le Crocus, &amp; la Rose,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Iris, l’Hyacinte, &amp; le Lys ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puis s’envolant dans le pourpris","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De son petit Palais Rustique,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec grand soin elle s’applique","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À serrer tout ce doux butin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont le Serpolet &amp; le Thim,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Lavande, &amp; la Marjolaine","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rendent enfin sa Ruche pleine.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le soir vint, son travail cessa","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand le Papillon, las, passa","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Auprés de l’Abeille chargée","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des dons de la douce Rosée.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il luy dit. Esprit mal tourné,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Né sous un Astre infortuné.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[73]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy ? perdre une telle journée,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[74]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans en l’air t’estre promenée !","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[75]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne m’en repens nullement,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Répondit-elle sagement.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aujourd’huy par mon industrie,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De miel je me trouve garnie,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont mon Maistre se nourrira,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la Cire me servira","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’offrande à la Troupe immortelle.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin, à mes emplois, fidelle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Donnant tout mon temps &amp; mes soins","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je sçay pourvoir à mes besoins.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais vous, à quoy s’est terminée","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cette heureuse, &amp; belle journée ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[87]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parlons avec sincerité.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[88]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le fruit de vostre oisiveté","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[89]/#"}},{"#":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" (","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#[1]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"chose qui vous doit déplaire","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#[3]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’estre fatigué sans rien faire.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[91]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Par cecy l’on voit nettement","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[92]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Combien est grand l’éloignement","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[93]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une Estude laborieuse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[94]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et d’une vaine &amp; curieuse.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[95]/#"}}]}}}}